<h4>Ms Dalmatia</h4>
<ul>
<li>Cabins: 19 (including 11 on deck)</li>
<li>Accommodates: 38/42 passengers</li>
<li>Built in: 2011</li>
<li>Crew: Captain, cook, waiter &amp; deck hands</li>
<li>Towels &amp; daily cabin cleaning included</li>
<li>Communal safe &amp; hairdryers available</li>
</ul>
